metadata.name: Unchecked Piracy
metadata.description: Inspired by Jack Butcher's Checks and his commitment to leveraging open editions for the sake of important work being done by nonprofits. All proceeds of this open edition will go directly to the 501C3 nonprofit WellBuilt Cities. They are investing in social infrastructure and social enterprises to build a city that works for all of its citizens, an economy that  nurtures sharing, an active & engaged citizenry, and prioritizes neighborliness.
